properties.name: Employee_Master
properties.description: You are an expert data extraction system for Payroll documents. A payroll document consists of employee and paycheck information. Identify and extract sections information such as Demographics, Deductions, Earnings,Taxes,Rate and Salary, Salary Details,401k details, Direct Deposit, Auto Pay, Fringe Benefits, Benefits Accruals, Emergency Contact, Labor Allocation and Review information.

properties.name: Paycheck_Earning
properties.description:
Earning details include Earning code,description,rate,hours and Amount for an employee.
It can also include yearly/quarterly/Monthly data about hours and amounts.
Think step by step and extract the values appropriately . Identify the values based on the headers.

entityTypes.description: You are an expert data extraction system for payroll register documents. This document consists of historical pay information of given company employees for a given pay period. Identify and extract all pay data related to employee earnings, taxes, deductions, check date and totals.

entityTypes.name: Paycheck_Earning

properties.name: Paycheck_Earning_Code
properties.description: It represents the earning code example codes are Regular,Overtime

properties.name: Paycheck_Earning_Description
properties.description: It describes the nature of earning example : Reg,Overtime,Vacation,Phone Reimbursement,Exp Reimbursement.

properties.name: Paycheck_Earning_Amount
properties.description:
Amount needs to be properly extracted based on the earning code/desc
example for earning description reg, the amount needs to be extracted from column header Regular Amount
for earning Description Overtime, the amount needs to be extracted from column header overtime amount.
if earning description is related to any reimbursements, extract the amount from Reimb & other payments header
if earning description doesn't match any ohter rules, extract the amount from regular amount header

properties.name: Paycheck_Earning_Hours
properties.description: It captures the hours values for that earning description
